		margin-top: 30px
		padding: 10px 0px
		border-bottom: 1px solid #F3F5F7
		font-weight: 600
		margin: 1.5em 0em 0.5em
		line-height: 1.2em
		color: #3A4652

	css h3
		font-size: 18px
		padding: 10px 0px
